extends layout

block styles
    //- Load Style(s) -//
    link(rel="icon" type="image/png" href="resources/favicon_home.png")

block header_content
    //- Topbar Centered Text -//
    div(class="ui item middle")
        div(class="ui center aligned container")
            div(class="ui large header") #{title}
    //- Topbar TU/e Logo -//
    div(class="ui item")
        div(class="ui right aligned container")
            a(href="https://www.tue.nl/en/")
                img(class="ui small image right floated tue_link" src="resources/tue_logo.png" onmouseover="pulseImage('tue_link')") 

block content
    //- Page Content -//
    div.content
        //- Large Logo -//
        img(class="ui large image centered" src="resources/logoETVIZnoQuote.svg" style="margin-top: 14px;") 
        //- About Segment -//
        div(class="ui floating raised segments")
            //- Redirecting Label -//
            div(class="ui segment")
                a(class="ui blue right icon big label" href="/about") About
                    i(class="ui info icon")
            //- Text Segment -//
            div(class="ui secondary segment")
                p This online tool was created by 5 Computer Science and Engineering students from the #[a(href="https://www.tue.nl/en/") University of Technology Eindhoven] as a student project.
                | 
                | For more information about the tool and eye tracking, visit the #[a(href="/about") about page].
        //- Visualization Segment -//
        div(class="ui floating raised segments")
            //- Redirecting Label -//
            div(class="ui segment")
                a(class="ui teal right icon big label" href="/visualization?id=default") Visualizations
                    i(class="ui eye icon")
            //- Text Segment -//
            div(class="ui secondary segment")
                p In our visualization tool we provide the following visualizations to the user. You can read more about these visualizations by clicking on them. This will redirect you on four different research papers dedicated to them.
                //- Visualization Type List -//
                div(class="ui grid")
                    div(class="four wide column")
                        button(class="ui tertiary button")
                            a(class="item" href="https://dl.acm.org/doi/pdf/10.1145/3356422.3356423") Eye Cloud
                    div(class="four wide column")
                        button(class="ui tertiary button") 
                            a(class="item" href="https://www.researchgate.net/profile/Michael_Burch2/publication/282899094_Gaze_Stripes_Image-Based_Visualization_of_Eye_Tracking_Data/links/5d00d4a492851c874c5fd47e/Gaze-Stripes-Image-Based-Visualization-of-Eye-Tracking-Data.pdf") Gaze Stripes
                    div(class="four wide column")
                        button(class="ui tertiary button") 
                            a(class="item" href="https://pdfs.semanticscholar.org/19f1/9b1c0f4e378b19acb3df3d32c44fa8490ced.pdf") Transition Graph
                    div(class="four wide column")
                        button(class="ui tertiary button") 
                            a(class="item" href="http://www.profitippliga.de/papers/58.pdf") Attention Map
                p Moreover, using the settings sidebar you can interact with the data. Therefore, you have more control over the visualizations, so you can discover patterns in the data.
        //- Upload Segment -//
        div(class="ui floating raised segments")
            //- Redirecting Label -//
            div(class="ui segment")
                a(class="ui green right icon big label" href="/upload") Upload
                    i(class="ui upload icon")
            //- Text Segment -//
            div(class="ui secondary segment")
                p Any user can upload their own dataset, allowing you to visualize your own data in this online visualization tool.

    //- Extend Page To Allow Scrolling -//
    footer(class="ui vertical footer segment")
        div(class="ui container")
            h1(class="ui header") 
            h1(class="ui header") 
            h1(class="ui header") 


block post_scripts
    //- Set Active Page to Home in 'navigation' Sidebar -//
    script.
        $('#index_nav').addClass('active');
        $('.pusher').css('overflow', 'scroll')
